Red Plait maintains his own page [in Russian] at 
    http://www.revers.forinfo.ru/
The files that he has sent are of interest to the 
linux reverse engineering community:

crackme.tgz          A crackme using RedPlait's packer
elf.rar              NASM patch to modify ELF file generation
elf_comp.static.gz   An elf file compressor
rpat-en.rar          A FLAIR preprocessor for linux libraries

